<% message.subject = "It's time to submit your delivery indicator #{'report'.pluralize(@invites.count)} on ReMIT" %>
Hi <%= @user.name %>,

It's time to submit your delivery indicator <%= "report".pluralize(@invites.count) %> on ReMIT.

The following <%= "link".pluralize(@invites.count) %> will take you to the <%= "form".pluralize(@invites.count) %> to complete your <%= "report".pluralize(@invites.count) %>:

<% @invites.each do |invite| %>
<%= invite.study.reference_number %> - <%= invite.study.title %> - <%= new_study_delivery_update_url(invite.study) %>?token=<%= @user.delivery_update_token %>
<% end %>

on the Médecins Sans Frontières ReMIT website.

Many thanks,

MSF ReMIT team.